{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "大婉带马如龙寻访“破碗”俞五。俞五原是江南俞家五太爷，又是丐帮帮主，富可敌国却藏身破饭馆后厨，以天下第一的吃喝本事和一只稀世柴窑破碗显出奇人风范。大婉透露小婉是邱凤城的情人，马如龙为寻小婉，答应陪俞五用大碗喝三天酒。三人围绕大碗、小碗、破碗不断调侃，最后大婉也加入酒局，马如龙在“三个醉鬼”的玩笑中想到自己无法逃避过错、歉疚与责任。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你是个好人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "以前我总觉得你有点不讲道理，现在才知道你是个好人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你怎知道我是个好人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我说不出，可是，我知道。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "来，我用大碗敬你一大碗。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你这个大婉，跟那个小婉有没有什么关系？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "可惜。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "为什么可惜？是不是因为你想看看那个小婉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我实在很想看看她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可惜你找不到她。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "可惜她不叫大婉。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这又有什么可惜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "如果她叫大婉我就比较容易找得到了，可惜她偏偏要叫小婉。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "叫大婉的女孩子绝不会太多，叫小婉的女孩子却绝不会太少，我只知道她叫小婉，叫我怎么去找？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你虽然找不到，总有人能找得到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "谁能找得到？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "今天你已经喝了几碗酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "喝了八碗，八大碗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你还能喝几碗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不知道的意思，就是还能喝很多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "不知道的意思，就是我喝酒通常都不用碗的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你用什么喝。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "用酒坛子。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你以为我是在吹牛？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "如果你酒量真的有这么好，我就可以带你去见一个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "去见谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "去见一个虽然从来不用小碗喝酒，却定能找到那个小婉的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "他用什么喝酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "用破婉。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "用破碗喝酒的人，就叫做破碗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "想不到你居然越来越聪明了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你说的这个破碗，是不是'破碗'俞五？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "除了他还有谁呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "贫无立锥，富可敌国，名满天下，无人识得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你能找得到他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我找不到，谁找得到。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你知道他在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "其实你应该知道的，他当然是在吃饭喝酒。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fan_guan_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "想不到，想不到，实在想不到。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fan_guan_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "你想不到我会来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fan_guan_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "能够见到姑娘的芳驾光临，我这一辈子也不算白活了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fan_guan_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老头子",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "五爷就在后面的厨房里，姑娘请随我来。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这老头本来是我们家厨房里的一个小厮，我们家的规矩一向很大。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "难道你们家的下人看见你时都要吻你的脚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "好像连皇宫大内，都没有这种规矩。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "他就是江南俞五？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "除了他，还有谁？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "是你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "想不到五爷还认得我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你是不是已经喝过酒？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "喝了一点。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "好，好极了，我正想找个人来陪我喝酒。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "喝酒就像是下棋，一定要两个人喝才有趣。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "三个人喝比两个人更有趣，我另外还找了一个人来陪你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "他也喝酒？也能喝？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "听说他的酒量还不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你听谁说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "听他自己。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "他说的话你都相信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "你为什么不自己试试？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "好，好极了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "好碗。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你看得出这是个好碗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "这是柴窑烧的，而且是最好的那一窑烧出来的，除了皇宫大内外，现在普天之下，绝对找不出第三个这样的碗来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不错，这种碗天下的确只有两个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "想不到你居然很有眼力，不但看人有眼力，看碗也有眼力。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "他看人，倒未必有眼力。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "他看人若没有眼力，怎么会看上了你。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你们来找我，当然并不是为了要来陪我喝酒的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "我想找一个人，可是我找不到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你是不是想我替你找？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你要找谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "我只知道她叫小婉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "小碗不如大碗，你既然有个大碗，为什么要找小碗？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "小碗为什么不如大碗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "无论装酒装药，小碗都没有大碗装得多，小碗当然不如大碗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "破碗呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "破碗就比大碗更好。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "一个碗若是破了，必定已尝遍了酸甜苦辣，就像是一个人，也要历尽风霜才会老，老人总比小孩的经验丰富，姜也是老的辣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "所以破碗当然比大碗更好。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "幸好我们说的是人，不是碗，这个小婉不但比大碗好，也比破碗好。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "我知道，这个小婉一定是个很美很美的女孩子，而且又温柔，又多情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你怎么知道的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "因为她是邱凤城的情人，银枪公子喜欢的女孩子，当然不会是我这样的丑八怪。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "原来这个小婉是别人的。难怪你肯要我替他去找。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们来做个交易。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "什么交易？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你在这里陪我用大碗喝酒，我替你去把这个小婉找到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "三天之内，我一定有消息告诉你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "我就在这里，陪你喝三天。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "用大碗喝？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "我喝几碗你就喝几碗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你知不知道我最大的本事是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我最大的本事就是吃饭，喝酒，睡觉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "吃饭，睡觉，我没有把握，喝酒我倒可以跟你比一比。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你不怕醉？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "醉死了我也要喝。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "好，好极了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "我出来的时候，我妈妈再三叮咛我，叫我千万不要喝醉酒，也千万不要去惹喝醉了的人，她说，天下的醉鬼都是一样的，不但自己神智不清，对别人也蛮不讲理。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan_mu_qin",
      "speaker_name": "大婉妈妈",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "天下的醉鬼都是一样的，不但自己神智不清，对别人也蛮不讲理。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你妈妈是个最聪明的女人，她说的话你一定要记住。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "男人喝醉了酒，是什么事都做得出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "所以她说，一个聪明的女人，遇到了一个醉鬼时，最好的法子就是赶快溜之大吉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan_mu_qin",
      "speaker_name": "大婉妈妈",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "一个聪明的女人，遇到了一个醉鬼时，最好的法子就是赶快溜之大吉。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "有理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "非常有理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "两个醉鬼当然比一个醉鬼更糟。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "有理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "天下惟一比一个人喝醉了更糟的就是两个人都喝醉了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "只可惜现在我就快要遇见两个醉鬼了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "在哪里？两个醉鬼在哪里？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "好像就在这里，就在我面前。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "我妈妈只告诉我，遇见一个醉鬼时，应该赶快溜之大吉，却没有告诉我遇见两个醉鬼时该怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "幸好我自己倒想出个法子。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "什么法子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "我自己也喝醉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "等我自己也变成醉鬼的时候就不怕醉鬼了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "有理。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "只有一点不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "哪一点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "三个醉鬼是不是比两个醉鬼更糟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "天下惟一比两个醉鬼更糟的，恐怕就是三个醉鬼了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "现在我就遇见了三个醉鬼。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "因为这三个醉鬼中，有一个就是我自己。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    }
  ],
